videos.description: Xavier's Paul Scruggs uses a nice bounce pass to set up Tyrique Jones for a monster slam on the fast break.
videos.headline: Scruggs sets up Jones for powerful dunk

videos.description: Paul Scruggs tosses up a lob and Zach Hankins goes up to throw it down to cap the fast break.
videos.headline: Hankins dunks the fast-break lob from Scruggs

videos.description: Quentin Goodin bolts down the lane and takes off to throw down a vicious slam over a defender.
videos.headline: Goodin slams ferociously on defender in the lane
